#ROOM
Vnum     38550
Name     &xThe Thondroril River - West Bank&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The bridge from the Western Plaguelands ends here. The water of the 
Thondroril River is dark and stagnant, moving with a sluggish, 
oily rhythm. The air becomes noticeably colder as you step onto 
the eastern bank, and the sky is a permanent shade of bruised 
orange. A wide, cracked road leads east into the heart of the 
blight.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    38103
Desc      Return to the Western Plaguelands.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    38551
Desc      The path leads into the Eastern Plaguelands.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38506 5 38550
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38551
Name     &xThe Marris Stead - Entrance&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A large farmhouse and several outbuildings sit atop a low hill. 
Unlike the other ruins in the Plaguelands, these buildings are 
remarkably well-maintained. Several large plaguehounds prowl 
the perimeter, and the air carries the scent of sharpened 
steel and wet fur.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    38550
Desc      Return to the river.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    38552
Desc      Toward the Marris Farmhouse.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    38553
Desc      Toward Corin's Crossing.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38502 5 38551
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38552
Name     &xThe Marris Farmhouse&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The interior of the farmhouse is clean and functional. Nathanos 
Blightcaller stands near a large fireplace, cleaning a 
massive black longbow. His red eyes track your movement 
with cold, predatory efficiency.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    38551
Desc      The stead entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38507 1 38552
  Reset G 1 38532 1
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38553
Name     &xCorin's Crossing - West&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     Once a thriving trade hub at the center of the Plaguelands, 
Corin's Crossing is now a graveyard of stone and bone. 
The buildings are shattered, and the streets are filled 
with the ghosts of the former residents.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    38551
Desc      The Marris Stead.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    38554
Desc      Corin's Crossing East.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    38555
Desc      The road to Stratholme.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38522 5 38553
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38554
Name     &xCorin's Crossing - East&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    ~
Desc     The eastern side of the trade hub is dominated by a large, 
ruined inn. The air here is stagnant and the sound of 
distant wailing is constant. A Scourge plague cauldron 
sits in the center of the town square.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    38553
Desc      Corin's Crossing West.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    38558
Desc      Toward Light's Hope Chapel.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38500 5 38554
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38555
Name     &xThe Road to Stratholme - South&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     A wide, soot-covered road leading north. To the east, the 
mountains rise high into the smoke, while to the west, 
the blighted forest stretches toward the horizon. 
Massive abomination-parts are seen in the ditches.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    38553
Desc      Return to Corin's Crossing.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    38556
Desc      The road continues north.~
