Reset M 0 38503 5 38555
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38556
Name     &xThe Road to Stratholme - North&d~
Sector   field~
Flags    ~
Desc     The road turns sharply to the west as it approaches the massive 
white stone walls of the city. The sky here is dark with the 
smoke of eternally burning buildings.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    38555
Desc      The southern road.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
