Reset M 0 38514 1 38556
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     38563
Name     &rThe Gates of Stratholme&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand before the massive, iron-bound gates of the once-great 
city of Stratholme. Fire still licks at the shattered wooden 
doors, and the smell of burning flesh is overwhelming. A 
shimmering white portal glows within the main gate, while 
high above, the shadow of a massive necropolis—Naxxramas—blots 
out the sickly orange sky.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    38556
Desc      Return to the road.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 38515 5 38563
Reset O 0 38552 1 38563
Reset O 0 38553 1 38563
#ENDROOM

